    CertificationCommand
    public static class CertificationCommand.FlushUnPersistedCommandsException
extends GeneralException
    This is an exception that will get thrown if there are commands that are in queue to be merged, but have not been persisted yet. This exception is broken out of GeneralException because in some cases it represents a problem that does not need to be worried about. So this is an attempt to be more specific about which exceptions are allowed.
